OL,3,CPolice protection for Paddington after
OL,4,Che's found dumped in park
OL,6,FNo, he's not about to be jailed again
OL,7,Ffor a crime he didn't commit -
OL,8,FPaddington is only in police custody
OL,9,Ffor his own protection.
OL,11,FThe much loved bear was found
OL,12,Fabandoned in Southampton's East Park
OL,13,Fearly on Sunday morning, following
OL,14,Freports he'd been taken from his bench
OL,15,Fin Guildhall Square.
OL,17,FThe theft occurred just days after the
OL,18,Fsculpture was re-installed, following
OL,19,Fa previous act of vandalism.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
