OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777911070
OL,3,CPolice protection for Paddington after
OL,4,Che's found dumped in park
OL,6,FOn a Facebook post, Southampton Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Thankfully, he was found in one
OL,8,Fpiece - and he certainly needed a
OL,9,Fmarmalade sandwich after his ordeal.
OL,11,F"While we know Paddington is a much-
OL,12,Floved character and this may raise a
OL,13,Fsmile, damage to public property is a
OL,14,Fserious offence.
OL,16,F"The statue brings joy to residents,
OL,17,Fvisitors, families and businesses in
OL,18,Fthe city centre, and it is
OL,19,Fdisappointing to see him targeted
OL,20,Fagain so soon after recent repairs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
