CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1777911070
OL,3,CPolice protection for Paddington after
OL,4,Che's found dumped in park
OL,6,F"Please look after Paddington. He is a
OL,7,Fbear of very good standing in our city"
OL,9,FThey are now reviewing CCTV and asking
OL,10,Fanyone with information to come
OL,11,Fforward.
OL,13,FPaddington first arrived in
OL,14,FSouthampton in October 2024 as part of
OL,15,Fa UK-wide trail celebrating the
OL,16,Frelease of 'Paddington in Peru'.
OL,18,FHe was originally placed near the
OL,19,FWestquay Shopping Centre but later
OL,20,Fmoved to Guildhall Square.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/3
